abstract: >
  This repository contains the implementation of a multimodal speech-based
  emotion recognition system developed as a senior graduation project.
  The project explores classical machine learning, deep learning, and
  state-of-the-art pretrained speech models using advanced acoustic feature
  extraction and rigorous evaluation protocols on the MELD dataset.

